bug.short_desc: 'Compare With Public Version' link is available for add-ons in full review queue

long_desc.thetext:
Created attachment 524223 screenshot
steps to reproduce: 1. Upload a new add-on to the full review queue 2. From Editor tools, access the review detail page for that add-on(https://addons.allizom.org/en-US/editors/review/763714?num=15) 3. Notice the 'Files and Validation Results' section
expected behavior: Nominated add-ons do not have the 'Compare With Public Version' link.
observed behavior: 'Compare With Public Version' link is available for add-ons in full review queue
I think andy added this last week
